cleaned_desc: 有一种大唐文化交流的感觉 还是比较希望能看到些有用的英语内容比如介绍文化的上才艺的展示美好身体的分享冷知识的炫耀宠物的而不是仅仅在自我介绍 我看到很多人帮忙做英语题来作为买路费大大滴好赞R 这也是一个非常好的传播中国文化的机会虽然感觉老外们不一定会在这里停留多久但能聊几分钟是几分钟有什么对中国好奇的事情都可以问大家一起分享不同的文化刚刚看到一个喜爱钩织的女孩问中国的钩织是不是有不同的图案我们希望多多出现这样的内容 机翻致歉 There is a feeling of cultural exchange in the Tang Dynasty I still hope to see some useful content such as introducing culture showing talents beautiful bodies sharing cold knowledge pets rather than just self introduction Many people helping with English homework as a way to pay for their travel expenses which is great This is a great opportunity to spread Chinese culture Although it feels like foreigners may not stay here for long they can chat for a few minutes Anything curious about China can be asked Lets share different cultures together I just saw a girl who likes crocheting and asked if there are different patterns in Chinese crocheting We hope to see more such content kissR kissR kissR
